quote_last: And he said, “O man greatly loved, fear not, peace be with you; be strong and of good courage.” And as he spoke to me, I was strengthened and said, “Let my lord speak, for you have strengthened me.”
title: Daniel
author: ESV

quote_last: When words are many, transgression is not lacking, but whoever restrains his lips is prudent.
title: Proverbs
author: ESV
